主播给予创作补贴。委员建议：直播打赏建立“消费冷静期”，设上限，无条件撤回！"},"attached_info":"CkEInr7+stmnzIVAEAMaCTExMzg5MjA1NiCM/7m+BjAAOD1AEHILMTQ1NzY0OTYzNjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"91 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5323183a2054b673d61b0b799a5a878a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"17_1741616470.581824","card_id":"Q_14246672300","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":14246672300,"title":"“我不跟你吵”的终止为什么让人感觉难受？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14246672300","type":"question","created":1741257550,"answer_count":30,"follower_count":34,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1576,3146,3946,15489,177476],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"昨天跟一个不是非常非常熟的朋友去吃饭，当在前往餐厅的路上，我们讨论到了某个话题（类似“xx广场在A区还是在B区”的问题），具体是什么我也记不清了（可见是个无聊的话题）。我们持对立的观点，当我想要进一步“据理力争”“xx广场在A区”的时候，他说“我不跟你吵”，停止了这个对话。 我的固执地“自证”被停止与对话停止后的沉默，让我有一拳打到棉花上的感觉。我知道他是想停止这样无意义的话题与争辩，是非常合理、理性的，但我却感觉有点难过，这是为什么呢？"},"attached_info":"CkEInr7+stmnzIVAEAMaCTExMzgyNTE0NCDO9qW+BjAAOCJAEXILMTQyNDY2NzIzMDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"67 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-10d3030597007d7b69750f93a82006b2_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1741616470.582415","card_id":"Q_13779140918","target":{"id":13779140918,"title":"孩子二年级想要邀请同学来给自己过生日，我该同意吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/13779140918","type":"question","created":1740840627,"answer_count":63,"follower_count":109,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https: